    <para id="id38997507">When Q is very high which is true for crystal then R<sub>e</sub>~0.</para>
    <para id="id39331749">And <figure id="id36275311"><media id="id36275311_media" alt=""><image mime-type="image/png" src="../../media/graphics25-1047.png" id="id36275311__onlineimage" height="34" width="74"/></media></figure></para>
    <para id="id49218929">In near future, we will have a Paradigm Shift. The scaling of CMOS will hit the wall. For that day we are developing ‘ MICROELECTROMECHANICAL SYSTEM(M E M S)’,Molecular Electronics &amp; Nanotechnology.</para>
    <para id="id49218934">We have to replace low Q integrated capacitor &amp; inductors. These will be replaced by MEMS structure. MEMS &amp; CMOS will enable highly efficient single chip radio.</para>
    <para id="id46318618">In 2002 Hewlett-Packard &amp; HCLA announced a molecular array with 100nm center to center memory element spacing(9/10/02)</para>
    <para id="id34031444">If we achieve 35nm center to center we will achieve 100 Gb memory space in 1(cm)<sup>2</sup>.</para>
    <para id="id45546140"/>
